//////BS Typography////////////////////////////////////

default font-size is 14px
default line-height of 1.428
<p> bottom margin (10px by default)

Font Size
------------
h1 Bootstrap heading (36px)
h2 Bootstrap heading (30px)
h3 Bootstrap heading (24px)
h4 Bootstrap heading (18px)
h5 Bootstrap heading (14px)
h6 Bootstrap heading (12px)
<small> lighter text
<mark> highlight text

Document
-----------------
<abbr> abbreviation/meaning of a word

Blog Comment
-------------------
<blockquote> comment with commentor  (.blockquote-reverse)

Text
----------------
<code> defines a "section" in a document
<kbd> keyboard tag 
<pre> show the content as it is
.pre-scrollable : Makes a <pre> element scrollable
Text Color: .text-muted, .text-primary, .text-success, .text-info, .text-warning, and .text-danger
background colors: .bg-primary, .bg-success, .bg-info, .bg-warning, .bg-danger
Text Alignment: .text-left, .text-center, .text-right, .text-justify
Text Break: .text-nowrap
Text Small Case: .text-lowercase   //word
Text Upper Case: .text-uppercase  //WORD
Text Capitalized : .text-capitalize  //Word

List
-------
<dl>  description list work like <ul>
<dt> description title header  work like <th>
<dd> description  data

.list-unstyled : list style type none
.list-inline : list display in line

Table
---------
Table: .table, .table-striped, .table-bordered, .table-hover, .table-condensed, 
<tr class="success"> : background color ( .success, .danger, .info, .warning, .active)
.table-responsive : Responsive Tables

